            .accordion-item.border.mb-3.shadow-sm.rounded-3.overflow-hidden
              h2.accordion-header#headingThree
                button.accordion-button.collapsed.bg-white.text-dark.fw-bold(type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree")
                  | What types of tours do you offer?
              #collapseThree.accordion-collapse.collapse(aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion")
